name: Swampy Sultans of the Wood
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Swampy Sultans of the Wood are known for their exceptional deep forest flashmarble craftsmanship. Now a member of a group researching the intersection of Groodu and Rootmason magics, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
